<h3 id=3D"SolutionsArchitectureDocument:LoanProcessAutomationServiceModerni=
zationwithNotes-5.DataManagement&amp;PIIConsiderations">5. <strong>Data Man=
agement &amp; PII Considerations</strong></h3>
<p>Since PII exists in your databases, you must establish <strong>data mask=
ing</strong> or <strong>data sanitization</strong> when promoting or replic=
ating data from prod to non-prod environments:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Scrub PII data (names, SSNs, account numbers, etc.).</p></li>
<li>
<p>Create sanitized datasets for lower environments to comply with NCUA and=
 general security best practices.</p></li>
</ul>
